# TikTok Ads Event Streaming Integration Summary

This documentation details the TikTok Ads Event Streaming integration that allows real-time streaming of Amplitude event data to TikTok Ads via the TikTok Events API, enabling improved ad targeting, conversion tracking, and campaign optimization through first-party behavioral data synchronization.

